            <title>[LU-10141] Integer overflow in llapi_changelog_start</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10141</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When reading changelogs from a high (more than 32bits) offset, the return value from lseek() is not properly interpreted and spurious errors can occur.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ex. w/ robinhood:&lt;br/&gt;
ERROR -95 opening changelog for MDT &apos;lustre-MDT0000&apos;: Operation not supported&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
